:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500205307-->
:::'''Mare:''' Huh? How did you know that?
:::'''Mare:''' Cats... How can anyone resist cats? They are so cute and charming, and their purring even helps with sleep.
:::'''Mare:''' Pity I have no time to look after a real cat... But I collected lots of cat videos, stickers, and photos. Just looking at them makes me happy.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} You've always been researching Aeons?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500205311-->
:::'''Mare:''' Mmm, but it's all a bit superficial, like reading and writing research papers.
:::'''Mare:''' I am very interested in everything related to the Aeons, but there are too many materials to read... I don't know when I can finish them all.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Do you have any books to recommend?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500205314-->
:::'''Mare:''' Books? I do read... a lot, but those books are all related to Aeons.
:::'''Mare:''' The series The Fall of The Aeons – A Discussion on Cosmic Traditions is pretty good and easy to understand. It's just a bit long...
:::'''Mare:''' Examples of Cosmic Legends: A Collection of Aeon References in Myths is also quite good. You can try that book when you have time.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} I don't think I have anything to ask.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500205319-->
:::'''Mare:''' Okay. You can come find me again if you have any other questions about the Aeons.
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission not Finish: 200030405-->)
