::{{DIcon|Talk}} Who is the lord you were talking about?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500010519-->
:::'''Mare:''' Oh! Are you also interested in the invasion? That was a huge event!
:::'''Mare:''' The enemies in the Legion are cosmic weapons made of antimatter. Do you know what that means?
:::'''Mare:''' It echos the infatuation and disaster in the Mystic Scroll of Aeons! As a result, I've come to this conclusion...
:::'''Mare:''' These invaders are followers of Nanook the Destruction! This can't be wrong!
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} What is the Mystic Scroll of Aeons?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500010524-->
:::'''Mare:''' It's a long story. You can say it's a record of cultures related to Aeons.
:::'''Mare:''' It is written in a very obscure fashion. Even though I've spent countless days and nights studying it, I can only understand a fraction of its philosophy.
:::'''Mare:''' But one very important thing is that the content of the Mystic Scroll of Aeons is based on facts, not groundless fabrications.
:::'''Mare:''' This Legion is the best way to prove this!
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Have you seen that lord?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500010529-->
:::'''Mare:''' Have I seen that lord? What are you talking about?
:::'''Mare:''' In ancient times, people were not aware of the exact nature of the sun but they still worshiped the Sun God. For them, the idea of approaching the scorching sun is too much for them to handle.
:::'''Mare:''' I am already happy that I managed to find clues about the existence of Aeons.
:::'''Mare:''' If... If I am really being watched by the great Aeons... Heheh...
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} I don't think I have anything to ask.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500010534-->
:::'''Mare:''' Please contact me if you have any other clues about the Aeons!
:::'''Mare:''' Preferably right away, and only me!
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
